Antonia D. Reed (amezaliwa Aprili 22, 1966), anajulikana kwa jina la kitaaluma kama Bahamadia, ni msanii muziki wa hip hop kutoka Marekani. 
Bahamadia alitoa albamu yake ya kwanza, Kollage, mwaka wa 1996, [1] ikifuatiwa na EP BB Queen iliyotolewa kwa kujitegemea mwaka wa 2000. 
Kisha akatoa albamu ya urefu kamili, Good Rap Music, mwaka wa 2005. 
Bahamadia pia ametoa wimbo "Dialed Up Vol. 
1" (mnamo 2013), "Hapa" (mnamo 2015), na "Dialed Up Vol. 
2" (mnamo 2018. ) 
Bahamadia amekuwa akishirikiana na na wasanii wengine wakiwemo The Roots, Jedi Mind Tricks, Erykah Badu, Morcheeba, Guru, na Towa Tei, na wengine wengi. 
Mnamo Novemba 2016, Bahamadia alionekana kama mgeni mwalikwa katika msimu wa 15 wa Project Runway, ambapo mwanawe, Mah-Jing Wong, alikuwa mshiriki. 
She was a music DJ in house parties around Philadelphia. ] She gained attention from Guru of Gang Starr in 1993 for her song on the EP Funk Vibes.[1] 
