(Shanachie) 2004: Change (Ruf) 2006: New Used Car (Ruf) 2007: Time Bomb (akiwa na Deborah Coleman, Roxanne Potvin) (Ruf) 2009: Queen Bee: Mkusanyiko wa nyimbo za Antone 2010: He Said She Said (akiwa na Peter Karp) (Blind Pig) 2012: Beyond the Crossroads (akiwa na Peter Karp) (Blind Pig) 2018: The Ice Queen (Stony Plain 1398; Dixiefrog 8803) 2021: Pinky's Blues (Stony Plain 1430) 
